I wrote this trick to solve..

```js
const data = [[1,2,3],[4,5,6],[7,8,9]]

const start = ws.actualRowCount
for (let r = 0; r < data.length; r++) {
    for (let c = 0; c <= data[r].length; c++) {
        ws.getRow(start+r+1).getCell(c+1).value = data[r,c]
    }
}
```
